column5: Hey all, Just an FYI that the public registration just opened for the Stoco Lake Crappie tournament. There are about 20 spots left. Awesome event, great payouts/prizes. Register ASAP as this tournament fills FAST. www.stocolakecrappie.com
never fished there but have followed their events...might have to try the lake one day

It's a great lake and event! My buddy has fished it since day 1, and I've fished it the last 3 years. Always a great time and highly recommend it to anyone. There only a few spots left, it's filling up fast!
dang just the wrong weekend or I would have given this a go for something to do!
